Running refrigerator missing, search begins
Police have begun searching for a lost refrigerator last seen running down Brand Highway.
/images/refrigerator.png
The last sighting of the refrigerator, captured by CCTV cameras last Monday.
text
An unidentified household refrigerator was seen running away on the east coast of Dongara last Monday. Law enforcements, led by Sergeant Carpenter, began efforts to search for the refrigerator the moment it was reported missing by its owner.

